content_text: My best friends name is Shut Up and he is my childhood friend and ever since we were in 5th class we have decided to do almost everything together and then we are always together. And he is a very good motivator. He always really motivated. Even when I am demotivated at work or if anything happens in my life, in my personal life, he always cheers me up and he always gives me hope that everything is going to be OK one day and he is really a very good speaker also so.
